reviewText: Wide screen version of swamp Thing wouln't play
love Lake Placid. the other 2 are good movies.

The Alligator People with Swamp Thing and Lake Placid?! What kind of sick mind would do that?! The Alligator People suck real badly, that it doesn't deserve to be a double feature with Swamp Thing and Lake Placid! Sure, Swamp Thing had a few wired things in it, Lake Placid is awesome that I enjoy it. But The Alligator People movie is a load of crap! It's no where of being good like The Mole People! This DVD is nothing more but crappy junk!
Saw these years ago. Always enjoyed strange movies. The Swamp Thing was the best one of the three movies on this DVD.
Gave as gift...recipient said this: "Alligator People was good sci-fi horror show, Lake Placid was top notch, Swamp Thing was a classic". Old campy "horror" movies that are still fun to watch!
